The paper deals with person re-identification using visual appearance, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The proposed framework involves attention mechanisms and feature composition, which are common techniques in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of human pose estimation, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM) and computer graphics (cs.CR).
